# Dental Career Opportunities

![Build Status](https://github.com/459ecs/dental-career-opportunities/actions/workflows/publish.yml/badge.svg)
![License](https://img.shields.io/github/license/459ecs/dental-career-opportunities)
![Quarto](https://img.shields.io/badge/Quarto-1.7.34-blue)

A professional career portal for Dr. Phoebe Tsang's pediatric dental practice, built with Quarto.

## 🌐 Live Site

**https://pedodontist.quarto.pub/dental-career-opportunities/**

## 📋 About

This repository powers a comprehensive job portal featuring:
- Multiple dental position listings (Certified Dental Assistant, Procedural Sedation Nurse, Treatment Coordinator)
- Detailed qualification requirements and assessments
- Automated IELTS speaking level testing integration
- Progressive disclosure UX for applicant-friendly experience
- DRY (Don't Repeat Yourself) architecture with single source of truth

## 🏗️ Built With

- **[Quarto](https://quarto.org/)** - Static site generator
- **GitHub Actions** - Automated publishing pipeline
- **Quarto Pub** - Hosting platform

## 🚀 Publishing

The site automatically publishes to Quarto Pub when changes are pushed to the `main` branch via GitHub Actions.

### Automated Workflow

1. Push changes to `main` branch
2. GitHub Actions triggers Quarto rendering
3. Site publishes to Quarto Pub automatically
4. Live site updates within 1-2 minutes

## 📁 Repository Structure

```
.
├── index.qmd                           # Main career portal (single source of truth)
├── certified_dental_assistant.qmd      # CDA position details
├── procedural_sedation_nurse.qmd       # PSN position details
├── treatment_coordinator.qmd           # TC position details
├── styles.css                          # Custom styling
├── _quarto.yml                         # Quarto configuration
├── .github/workflows/publish.yml       # CI/CD pipeline
└── CLAUDE.md                           # Development documentation
```

